data.description: HEY ALL BACK ON THE MARKET Find your private oasis at 520 N Ballard Rd. Charming home on a quiet street with an enormous yard to relax in while watching the deer graze the grass and escape into the woods. This 3 bedroom 2 bath home offers an open floor plan with a soaring ceiling in the living room. The modern kitchen boasts a s center island and plenty of storage space. The primary bedroom includes a trey ceiling and a gorgeous en-suite bathroom with dual vanity and a soaking tub to relax in. 2 additional guest bedrooms provide plenty of space to fit your needs. This home offers stunning spaces to entertain inside and out!  5000$ lending credit with preferred lender.
